{
  "stem": "2133.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he tried to see that maybe-- [SIGHS], that I should stay there and he would be able to look after me.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But his promise, couldn't keep it because one day they came and they took me to work.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So again, put me into the wagons.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But the main time when I was there, [SIGHING], the people told me that they used to have appells there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I haven't seen-- we had the appells that you have to stand always.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That they usually have appells there that they would take the hose in a freezing time, and they hosed the people down until they were frozen and died right there.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But I did see that one of the prisoners supposed to snitch somebody's bread or something.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the other prisoners took him, and they throw him right into the outhouse.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They didn't have the bathrooms.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They had those outhouses.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They threw him right inside to that outhouse.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was the most terrible thing to see.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I mean, you couldn't even climb out from that, because it was quite large for that many people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So as I said, after a week, they needed people to work, so they took me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we went, again, traveled for about three, four days.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I don't quite remember the names of the towns, because I really was in a haze.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't know where I was or what-- what next.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I just went along whatever I was told to do.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we arrived to this little town.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were all put into the horse barn.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That's where we were living.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "A horse barn?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A horse barn.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was animals-- horses-- was--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so we stayed there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And every single day, we went to work in a gasoline refinery.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
